@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.31)))
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.70 + v1 + 0.73)) - wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.26)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.04 / v0 + 0.11)) * (wp.abs(tmp + 0.11) * (v2 + 0.60 * v2 + 0.74)))
    v1 = wp.exp(0.23)
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.sin(v1 + 0.65) + (v0 + 0.54 - tmp + 0.59)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.63) - v2)
    v2 = (0.63 - ((v2 + 0.91 * v1 + 0.04) * (v2 + 0.60 + v0 + 0.90)))
    data[tid] = v0
